snippet.title: Pranking My Teacher With The World's HOTTEST Pepper!
snippet.description:
Pranking My Teacher With The World's Hottest Pepper | The Frustrated Gamer Bash The Teacher game is back with a new game called Feed the School game! We're working in the school cafeteria and need to give the students and teacher exactly what they want. Let's play Feed the School Chili Chaos gameplay with The Frustrated Gamer! 
#Bashtheteacher #feedtheschool #frustratedgamer 

► https://youtu.be/mBPnaPztOeU
